 Data Cleaning & Reporting Automation

Project Overview

This project focuses on automating data cleaning and reporting processes to improve data quality and reporting efficiency.

 Objectives

* Clean and preprocess raw datasets.
* Handle missing values and duplicate records.
* Standardize inconsistent data formats.
* Generate automated reports and summaries.
* Improve workflow efficiency through automation.

 Key Features

* Data cleaning automation.
* Missing value handling.
* Duplicate record removal.
* Data validation and standardization.
* Automated report generation.
* Visual summaries and insights.

 Tools Used

* Python
* Pandas
* NumPy
* Excel
* Power BI

 Methodology

1. Import raw data.
2. Identify missing values and duplicates.
3. Clean and standardize the dataset.
4. Validate data quality.
5. Generate summary reports.
6. Create visualizations for insights.

 Expected Outcome

Understand data preprocessing, automation techniques, and efficient reporting workflows.

## Conclusion

Automating data cleaning and reporting improves data accuracy, saves time, and supports better decision-making through reliable data analysis.
